## 1. Purpose

This log records significant design and architecture decisions made during the {{PROJECT_NAME}} project, using the DAR (Decision Analysis and Resolution) approach from CMMI v3.0. Each entry documents alternatives considered, evaluation criteria with weights, and the selected option — ensuring decisions are traceable and auditable.

DAR trigger criteria are defined in `docs/pal/dar-trigger-criteria.md`. Not every decision requires a DAR entry — only those meeting the trigger threshold (cost, risk, irreversibility, stakeholder impact).

